    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/63637a7dcfde65906459412a5ef3c121.avif?t=1759217937\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/f5df7be517c571abd354055598db2f68.poster.avif?t=1759217937\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/f5df7be517c571abd354055598db2f68.webm?t=1759217937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/f5df7be517c571abd354055598db2f68.mp4?t=1759217937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Bullet Noir》是一款双摇杆射击游戏。游戏中，你要潜入阴影，谨慎决定每一次行动，每发子弹都可能夺走你的生命。在这个冷酷无情的世界里，你将了解四名角色互相交织的故事，他们每个人都渴望为遇害的导师复仇，不达目的誓不罢休。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/4773dc303e9a740812ba2d4b993b7572.avif?t=1759217937\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流畅的双摇杆射击体验：你可以正面突击，也可以一路潜行。选择权在你。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情驱动的游戏玩法：通过扣人心弦的剧情探索四名不同角色的动机和背景故事。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特技能：掌握每名角色的独特技能以克服挑战，并发挥创意智取敌人。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >章节式结构：以多种视角体验剧情，每个章节的主题是不同角色的旅程。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑色美术风格：迷人的美术风格营造出黑暗残酷的氛围，令人沉浸其中。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >俯瞰一切：以俯视角在阴郁的城市里穿行，游戏玩法无情而有挑战性。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Bullet Noir》的故事发生在一个充斥着黑色的城市里，游戏以高对比度的荒凉艺术风格呈现引人注目的视觉体验。游戏的叙事丰富而有层次，向玩家展现将这些角色联系在一起的黑暗秘密以及私人恩怨。复仇是唯一的救赎之道。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/567afcc41a42ba51aec0692b0db4ee55.poster.avif?t=1759217937\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/567afcc41a42ba51aec0692b0db4ee55.webm?t=1759217937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/567afcc41a42ba51aec0692b0db4ee55.mp4?t=1759217937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/bfafbf4a9f3b7fa09042e26a5865d8f4.avif?t=1759217937\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Bullet Noir》里，复仇不仅仅是一项任务，还是生活方式。准备好潜入阴影，揭开真相了吗？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/3290340a0de1d41a2bd5ea975f77ffc2.poster.avif?t=1759217937\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/3290340a0de1d41a2bd5ea975f77ffc2.webm?t=1759217937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204960/extras/3290340a0de1d41a2bd5ea975f77ffc2.mp4?t=1759217937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
